	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg. pro pr., uncertain date. He is named with this title in an inscription of Mevania (CIL 11.5029) of late republican or early Augustan date. He perhaps earned the gratitude of Mevania in the period of Caesar's settlements of veterans (cf. Q. Valerius Orca, MRR 2.312) or under the triumvirate (RS, MS-RP 1.288).[181x]\n" .
